data.description: This charming 4BR/1BA home is nestled within a peaceful oasis, boasting a fenced-in yard enveloped by the natural beauty of towering trees. As you step inside this doll house, you'll be greeted by elegant luxury vinyl flooring that flows seamlessly throughout the entire home. The heart of this residence is its great room living space w/a recently installed electric fireplace and adorable eat-in kitchen w/white cabinets and stainless appliances. The split bedroom plan offers ample space for relaxation and rest, including a remodeled primary suite. One of the unique features of this property is the detached garage/workshop. It's a versatile space that can be utilized for parking, hobbyist's haven, a home gym, or simply used for storage. Beyond the walls of this delightful home, you'll find a peaceful deck, lush yard and above ground pool secured by a sturdy fence for privacy and peace of mind. The canopy of trees that surrounds the property provides shade and tranquility, turning the backyard into a natural retreat.
